            "title": "滬指開市跌3點 深成指跌25點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以3320點開市，跌3點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10592點，亦跌25點或0.24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌6點或0.17%，開報3906點；創業板指數開市報2174點，跌7點或0.35%。</p>\n</div>",
