            "title": "即月期指開報22819點 低水158點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報22819點，跌177點，較上日現貨收市價22976點低水158點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5589點，跌67點，低水50點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8413點，跌69點，低水62點。</p>\n</div>",
